@startuml
title Viaverse Job Lifecycle / Delivery Approval — Activity Diagram
start
:QuoteAccepted;
:Create Job draft;
:Wait for PaymentAuthorized;
if (Payment ok?) then (yes)
  :Set READY_TO_START;
  :Worker starts work;
  :Job workspace\nchat / media / updates;
  :Worker delivers work;
  :Requester reviews delivery;
  if (Approve delivery?) then (approved)
    :Set COMPLETED;
    :Mark payout eligible;
    :Trigger review prompt;
    :Emit JobCompleted;
    :Emit PayoutEligible;
  else (needs fix)
    :Request fix / revision;
    :Worker redelivers;
  endif
  if (Open dispute?) then (yes)
    :Create dispute case;
    :Block payout;
  endif
else (no)
  :Block start\npayment failed/retry;
endif
stop

note bottom
Auto-approval after timeout can be added later as configurable policy,
but dispute/report path must always be available before payout release.
end note
@enduml
